                <span class="female-character">Mama Merino</span>: "YOU'RE GONNA MAKE IT, BABY!"
            </div>

            <p>Judge Owl attended the ceremony. She approached Brer Sheep afterward.</p>

            <div class="dialogue">
                <span class="female-character">Judge Owl</span>: "Well, Mr. Sheep. Eighteen months ago, I sentenced you to a decade of hard labor."<br><br>
                <span class="character">Brer Sheep</span>: "Yes, Your Honor."<br><br>
                <span class="female-character">Judge Owl</span>: "And now you've completed one of the most intensive rehabilitation programs in the state."<br><br>
                <span class="character">Brer Sheep</span>: "Yes, Your Honor."<br><br>
                <span class="female-character">Judge Owl</span>: "Do you know what I think?"<br><br>
