                <span class="female-character">Sister Ewe</span>: "The best kind of boring."<br><br>
                <span class="character">Brer Sheep</span>: "Yeah. Hey, Sister Ewe? Thank you. For everything."<br><br>
                <span class="female-character">Sister Ewe</span>: "You did the work. I just showed you where to start."<br><br>
